      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 136,
      "message": "Didn't you want to wait for the policy-pap to be up ?\nThen it should look like:\n```\nreadinessCheck:\n  wait_for:\n    services:\n      - policy-pap\n```\nIf you want to additionally need to wait for the job, you can add:\n```\n    jobs:\n      - '{{ include \"common.release\" . }}-policy-pg-migrator-config'\n\n```",
